- **proptest**: Property-based tests for trait dispatch correctness — generate random sequences of register_hook/unregister_hook/fire_event calls and verify dispatcher invariants hold (no double-free of HookIds, events always reach all registered handlers, unregistered hooks never fire)
- **criterion benchmarks**: Measure trait method dispatch overhead through `dyn ScriptingEngine` vtable; target <10ns per dispatch call to ensure the abstraction layer adds negligible cost vs direct calls

